# Python Line Length

Keep each line of **source code** to a maximum of **79 characters**.

This matches `[tool.black] line-length`, `[tool.isort] line_length`, and
`.editorconfig` `[*.py] max_line_length` for this project. Docstrings and
comments have a separate limit (see docstring-line-length and
comment-line-length).

Wrap long statements over multiple lines. Break after binary operators,
commas, or parentheses so that continuation lines are clearly indented.
